description:
You might think the grass is greener in a better hotel room, but Judge Walsh decides how green it is. The trip planner of a friend group never got paid back for a hotel room she bought, but the friend claims the hotel policy clears her of paying. Judge Walsh cuts through the confusion to deliver justice. Plus, the bailiff brings on a special helper.
